x; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-size: 9px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; text-align: left;"><a href="http://www.fxguide.com/download/?force_file=/2013/08/BOSCH_TIGER_30.mp4" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(136, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; outline: none;">Download Video</a></span></div>\r\n	<hr class="clear" style="background-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); color: rgb(221, 221, 221); clear: both; float: none; width: 640px; height: 0px; margin: 0px; border: none; font-size: 1px; line-height: 0px; padding: 0px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;" />\r\n	<p class="wp-caption-text" style="margin: 0px 0px 4px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n		Watch the Bosch spot.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Verdana, ''Lucida Grande'', ''Gill Sans'', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);">\r\n	&ldquo;On top of that,&rdquo; adds Moure, &ldquo;the different plates that we made in all those frames in which man and tiger appeared together, we had to resolve in advance the extent of the laboratory. We did this with motion control in order to synchronize the movement of the camera with the different plates that they suggested, and we translated that information into our lab in CGI. This work brought a lot of joy to us, as it&rsquo;s a campaign that was made for more than six European countries.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<hr class="clear" style="background-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); color: rgb(221, 221, 221); clear: both; float: none; width: 683px; height: 0px; margin: 0px; border: none; font-size: 1px; line-height: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Verdana, ''Lucida Grande'', ''Gill Sans'', Arial, sans-serif;" />\r\n<div class="wp-caption alignleft" id="attachment_46092" style="margin: 4px 24px 20px 0px; padding: 4px; border: none; font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica, Verdana, ''Lucida Grande'', ''Gill Sans'', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline; float: left; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241); color: rgb(136, 136, 136); line-height: 18px; text-align: center; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; width: 298px;">\r\n	<a class="fx_colorbox cboxElement" href="http://www.fxguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Bosch_BEFORE_01.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(136, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; outline: none; position: relative; display: inline-block;"><img alt="Original plate." class="wp-image-46092 " height="162" src="http://www.fxguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Bosch_BEFORE_01-320x180.jpg" style="margin: 5px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" width="288" /></a>\r\n	<p class="wp-caption-text" style="margin: 0px 0px 4px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n		Original plate.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="wp-caption alignright" id="attachment_46094" style="margin: 4px 0px 20px 24px; padding: 4px; border: none; font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica, Verdana, ''Lucida Grande'', ''Gill Sans'', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline; float: right; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241); color: rgb(136, 136, 136); line-height: 18px; text-align: center; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; width: 298px;">\r\n	<a class="fx_colorbox cboxElement" href="http://www.fxguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Bosch_AFTER_01.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(136, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; outline: none; position: relative; display: inline-block;"><img alt="Final plate." class="wp-image-46094 " height="162" src="http://www.fxguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Bosch_AFTER_01-320x180.jpg" style="margin: 5px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" width="288" /></a>\r\n	<p class="wp-caption-text" style="margin: 0px 0px 4px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n		Final shot.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr class="clear" style="background-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); color: rgb(221, 221, 221); clear: both; float: none; width: 683px; height: 0px; margin: 0px; border: none; font-size: 1px; line-height: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Verdana, ''Lucida Grande'', ''Gill Sans'', Arial, sans-serif;" />\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Verdana, ''Lucida Grande'', ''Gill Sans'', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);">\r\n	A more futuristic laboratory setting was required for a commercial for Spanish pharmaceuticals company NORMON. That spot, which was also the first ad NORMON had even created for television, features Wimbledon champion Manolo Santana engaging in a virtual tennis match. &ldquo;We had to film it all against green, and handle the design, as well as the composition and supervision of the campaign,&rdquo; explains Moure. &ldquo;We decided to create a 3D set, and film it in order to be able to have previsualisation live, which aided us with the realization of the spot. Then we brought everything to WeWork to finish the exhausting job of extracting from the green, tracking of camera and replacement of elements.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<div class="wp-caption aligncenter" style="margin: 0px auto 20px; padding: 4px; border: none; font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica, Verdana, ''Lucida Grande'', ''Gill Sans'', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241); color: rgb(136, 136, 136); line-height: 18px; text-align: center; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; width: 640px;">\r\n	<div class="video-player" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 640px;">\r\n		<div class="mejs-container mejs-video" id="mep_1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial; vertical-align: top; position: relative; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left; width: 640px; height: 360px;">\r\n			<div class="mejs-inner" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n				<div class="mejs-mediaelement" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 640px; height: 360px;">\r\n					<div class="me-plugin" id="me_flash_1_container" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: absolute;">\r\n						&nbsp;</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n				<div class="mejs-layers" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n					<div class="mejs-poster mejs-layer" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 640px; height: 360px;">\r\n						<im